:::'''Prototype Garmentmaker:''' Now, perhaps it's time to reveal the full scope of Lady Aglaea's plan to you.
:::'''Prototype Garmentmaker:''' It began with a small-yet-noble ideal: to resist the black tide. To be precise, to survive it.
:::'''Prototype Garmentmaker:''' The esteemed guest is already aware of the devastation the black tide has wrought upon the land of Amphoreus. Neither humans nor strange beasts can survive its influence, only one thing is an exception.
