:::'''Prototype Garmentmaker:''' That's right. I believe the esteemed guest has also witnessed that the weavers are able to temporarily resist the invasion of the black tide. While they cannot move freely within it, the black tide indeed cannot completely engulf them.
:::'''Prototype Garmentmaker:''' This is the first step from nothing to something. If we can uncover the secrets behind the weavers' mystery, one day, the people of Amphoreus will no longer fear natural disasters.
:::'''Prototype Garmentmaker:''' But according to the current calculations, the number of nymphs required for the plan is far greater than what we can find. I have no idea where to obtain the remaining nymphs.
:::'''Prototype Garmentmaker:''' Regardless, thank you for your continued assistance.
